'''Newport State Park''' waa {{Convert|2373|acre}} Wisconsin state park oo ku taal cirifka Door Peninsula ee u dhow Ellison Bay, Wisconsin. Ilaalinta {{Convert|11|mi|km}} ee xeebta  ay ku taalo Harada Michigan, Newport waa Wisconsin waa xadiiqada keliya ee loogu talagalay  gobolka. Sannadkii 2017, Ururka Caalamiga ah ee Cirka ayaa Newport ugu magac daray Badbaadinta cirka.<ref>Lee Bergquist. "[http://www.jsonline.com/story/news/local/wisconsin/2017/06/07/newport-state-park-designated-dark-sky-park/375936001 Newport State Park designated as Wisconsin's first 'dark sky' park]". ''Milwaukee Journal Sentinel'', Juunyo 7, 2017.</ref> xadiiqada ayaa furan sanadka oo dhan<ref>[https://dnr.wi.gov/topic/parks/name/newport/ Newport State Park], ''Wisconsin DNR''</ref> waxaana laga heli karaa WIS 42.

== Kormeeraha wasakhda hawada ==
[[File:HYSPLITTrajectoriesforNewportStateParkpage72.jpg|thumb|left|upright=0.4|Khariidadda HYSPLIT 2016]]

Kormeeraha kaliya ee  kormeera wasakheynta hawada dadweynaha ee gobolka wuxuu ku yaal Xadiiqadda Gobolka Newport.<ref>Sawirka xarunta kormeerka ee bogga 128 ee [https://www.epa.gov/sites/production/files/2017-09/documents/wiplan2016.pdf Air Monitoring Network Plan 2016], Juunyo 2015, ''Wisconsin DNR''</ref> Badanaa wasakheynta hawada ee soo gaarta saldhigga waxay ka timaaddaa meel ka baxsan wadanka. Khariiradani waxa ay muujineysa sida hawadu ugu socoto saldhiga kormeerka. Sababta oo ah saldhiggu wuxu ku dhowyahay xeebta,  khadadka cas keliya (ayaa muujinaya hawo-mareenka hoose) waxay sawir macno leh ku muujinayeen jidka ozone ee kormeer-ka. Sida ku cad khariidada, hawadan hoose ee hadda waxay ka qaadaan hawo wasakhaysan magaalooyinka waaweyn. In ka fog iland, si kastaba ha ahaatee, hawada ka sareysa ayaa isku qasta in badan, sidaa darteed khadadka midabyada oo dhami waa kuwo muhiim ah marka la raad raacayo wadada wasakheynta hawada ee inbadan gudaha, iyo qulqulka hawada sare (oo lagu muujiyey cagaar iyo buluug) ayaa ka imanaya nadiifin, inta badan meelaha miyiga ah.<ref>[https://www.epa.gov/sites/production/files/2018-05/documents/wi_tsd_final.pdf Wisconsin: Northern Milwaukee/Ozaukee Shoreline Area, Sheboygan County Area, Manitowoc County Area, Door County Area Final Area Designations for the 2015 Ozone National Ambient Air Quality Standards Technical Support Document (TSD)], ''US EPA Green Book''</ref>
